Example on mkaing a project with Kivy, after you have read the tutorial document
and did a couple of exmaples from the folder Kivy_App_Tutorial_00, and made your own .py
examples.

You should be ready to make a couple of small projects with Kivy & Python
Feel free to check out these 3 projects as a reference.
All of this information has been compiled into these 3 small projects. So if your stuck find the issue and go
back to the category that the issue is from, and work it out from there.

If your still stuck feel free to check out
https://kivy.org/doc/stable/tutorials/firstwidget.html
if your still stuck then contact me on Discord for any assistance.
